                  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">
                    <tr>
                      <td><font size="3">Hawaii</font></td>
                      <td align="right"> <font size="3"><img src="../../img/flags/flg_usa.gif" width="66" height="35"></font></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" height="1">
                    <tr background="../../img/maps/cp_tile.gif" valign="top"> 
                      <td background="../../img/maps/cp_tile.gif"><img src="../../img/maps/cp_space.gif" width="37" height="1"></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <p class="profile_intro">Hawaii, the 50th state of the USA, 
                    is one of the main tourist destinations in the world, attracting 
                    more than 6 million visitors each year. Its population today 
                    is a melting pot of different cultures from all over the world: 
                    Americans from the mainland, Japanese, Filipinos, Chinese, 
                    Koreans, Samoans and native Hawaiians. 
                  <p align="center"><img src="../../img/maps/cp_hawaii.gif" width="474" height="305" alt="Map of Hawaii"></p><br>
                  <br>
